    <text>
        <body>
            
            
            <div xml:id="Regret"> 
                <interpGrp type="character">
                    <interp ana="#form" type="sonnet">sonnet</interp>
                    <interp ana="#tone" type="sad">sad</interp>
                    <interp ana="#topic" type="love">love</interp>
                </interpGrp>
                <p>I said a thoughtless word one day,</p>
                <p>A loved one heard and went away;</p>
                <p>I cried: “Forgive me, I was blind;</p>
                <p>I would not wound or be unkind.”</p>
                <p>I waited long, but all in vain,</p>
                <p>To win my loved one back again.</p>
                <p>Too late, alas! to weep and pray,</p>
                <p>Death came; my loved one passed away.</p>
                <p>Then, what a bitter fate was mine;</p>
                <p>No language could my grief define;</p>
                <p>Tears of deep regret could not unsay</p>
                <p>The thoughtless word I spoke that day.</p>
            </div>
            
